descript.abstract:
[Metadata] Coastline of the Northwest Hawaiian Islands (NWHI)Northwest Hawaiian Islands (French Frigate Shoals, Gardner Pinnacles, Kaula Rock, Kure Atoll, Laysa Island, Lisianski Island, Midway Islands, Necker Island, Nihoa Island, Pearl and Hermes Atoll).
Created by NOS National Geodetic Survey, 2001. Esri staff downloaded from NOS National Geodetic Survey, 2016.
For additional information, see metadata at https://files.hawaii.gov/dbedt/op/gis/data/coastline_nwhi.pdf, or contact the Hawaii Statewide GIS Program, Office of Planning, State of Hawaii; PO Box 2359, Honolulu, HI 96804; (808) 587-2846; email: gis@hawaii.gov; Website: https://planning.hawaii.gov/gis.
